  "name": "RPlog_Loki_s_Confession",
  "title": "Loki's Confession",
  "summary": "Aboard the Imperial Star Destroyer Inquisitor, ISB System Director Korynn Fleming reviews damning reports about the imprisoned pilot Loki before paying him a personal visit in the interrogation wing. After softening the prisoner with stormtroopers, Fleming enters the cell alone and confronts the defiant, suspended Loki with veiled threats about how easily treason takes root. The two trade barbs in a tense battle of wills, Fleming probing the pilot's loyalties while Loki struggles to master his anger and the dread growing within him. Fleming makes it clear that Loki will never return to active service, dangling the faint, false promise of leniency only if he cooperates. The confrontation leaves the pilot's fate hanging and his confession still to come.",
